body:
Responsibilities:

-Selects the best non-edited images;
-Retouches the non-edited images for further use;
-Handles storage for non-edited and retouched images;
-Saves the retouched images in the allocated folders(depending on product code);
-Saves periodically and in critical situations both non-edited and retouched images;
-Checks how images display on webshop;
-Keeps working relations with Creative responsible;
-Keeps up-to-date KPI's;

Candidate Profile:

-At least 1 year experience in photo editing;
-Solid knowledge of Adobe Photoshop;
-Good knowledge of English;
-Pro-active, attentive to details person (good eye for details);
-Good communication skills;
-High-speed person,rigorous, accurate,organized, working with short deadlines;
-Work in a fast-paced environment;
-preferably University Degree;
-Adaptable to a young team.
